descriptionHtml:
Hi Guys!

This is my personal tweak for NLA,and in my opinion its look better :D
I hope you guys like it!

Natural Lighting and Atmospheric
Enhanced Light FX
Realistic Water Two

[For Comparison]
First 3 images are "MY" preset
Last 3 images are "Original/Confidence-Man" preset

Requierement : Natural Lighting and Atmospherics for ENB (http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50065/)

Installation     : 1. Install all of NLA file,and then simply replace it with my file. *ENB 269
                         2. Open your enblocal.ini and look the [PROXY] section at the top,then overwrite it with this
EnableProxyLibrary=true
InitProxyFunctions=true
ProxyLibrary=d3d9_Sweetfx.dll
                      
Enjoy :D


*Check out my SweetFX preset for other games!
